**Example Code Structure:**\
```python\
def calculate_yield_spread(df: pd.DataFrame) -> pd.Series:\
    """\
    Calculate 10Y-3M Treasury yield spread.\
    \
    Args:\
        df: DataFrame containing yield_10y and yield_3m columns\
    \
    Returns:\
        Series with yield spread values\
    \
    Raises:\
        ValueError: If required columns are missing\
    """\
    if 'yield_10y' not in df.columns or 'yield_3m' not in df.columns:\
        raise ValueError("Missing required yield columns")\
    \
    return df['yield_10y'] - df['yield_3m']\
```\
